CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 25, 1960, pg. A11 reads: "6. J.W. Peake, owner, and C.J. Tappe, manager, kept a constant flow of men, women and children supplied with yardsticks in Acme Window Shade and Venetian Blind Co. booth"
TitMainTitle: J.W. Peake and C.J. Tappe standing in Acme Window Shade and Venetian Blind Company booth, in Syria Mosque for the 1960 Courier-WAMO Home-A-Rama
